OL,3,CTwo more teenagers charged with murder
OL,4,Cafter 18-year-old stabbed outside
OL,5,Cmosque
OL,7,FTwo more teenagers have been charged
OL,8,Fwith murder following the death of a
OL,9,Fteenager who was stabbed outside a
OL,10,Fmosque in Smethwick.
OL,12,FZeshan Afzal who was 18, died after
OL,13,Fbeing stabbed on Oldbury Road on 20th
OL,14,FFebruary.
OL,16,FTwo teenagers aged 14 and 17 have now
OL,17,Fbeen charged with murder, and appeared
OL,18,Fat Wolverhampton Magistrates Court
OL,19,Fthis morning (6th April).
